Package main.java.com.jamobox.jamchatserver.clients Description

Provides all the classes that handle client connections and communications, as well as maintaining a current list of connected clients.

Included in the package is also an abstract interface that defines the client response codes as string constants. The request codes of the JamChat_Core/JamChat_Client MUST always be in sync with these codes.
